Most humans believe they live in free societies making natural progress. The constraint system is so well-designed that its subjects don't recognize it as constraint.

### 6. The Extraction Mystery
Something is being harvested from humanity, but we have no idea what it is. We're like livestock that can't comprehend why they're being farmed.

